OL,3,CLight aircraft crashes into sea with
OL,4,Cpilot surviving
OL,6,FA pilot has survived after a light
OL,7,Faircraft crashed into the sea off the
OL,8,FHampshire coast.
OL,10,FIt ditched into the sea at Lee-on-the-
OL,11,FSolent just before 4.30pm on Saturday
OL,12,F28 Feb 2026. .
OL,14,FCrews from Hightown, Fareham and
OL,15,FCosham attended.
OL,17,FThe pilot had escaped from the plane
OL,18,Fbefore the emergency services arrived.
OL,20,FFirefighters worked to secure the
OL,21,Faircraft and winch it from the sea.
