OL,3,CLight aircraft crashes into sea with
OL,4,Cpilot surviving
OL,6,FHampshire & Isle of Wight Fire &
OL,7,FRescue Service said: "The pilot was
OL,8,Fassessed by the ambulance service and
OL,9,Fthe scene was handed over to our
OL,10,Fcolleagues at Hampshire & Isle of
OL,11,FWight Constabulary to maintain
OL,12,Fsecurity of the aircraft until it can
OL,13,Fbe recovered."
